<!--
Difinitions:
	field ... images to be displayed
	light ... definitions for lighs:
					  pos: Position on the 3x3 matrix
					  	1 2 4
					  1	x	x	x		=> val 1
					  2	x	x	x		=> val 2
					  4	x	x	x		=> val 3
						every light tag defines one light.
						signal: the signalisation status
							0 => stop (red)
							1 => go (green)
							2 => go with restriction ???
						status: status of the block
							0 => off
							1 => requested
							2 => occupied
						
-->

